          <header class="main-header content-section">
               <h1 class="main-header__title">About <span class="main-header__title--emphasize">NerdLevels</span></h1>
               <h4 class="main-header__subtitle">NerdLevels offer programming courses in video game and web development. Developed by teachers and programmers, our content focuses on programming with with technologies used and in demand by the industry. Unlike traditional programming courses all of our curriculum is project based. We provide you an authentic problem to solve, you design a high-quality solution, and we give you the information you need to make your vision come true.</h2>
          </header>

          <section class="curriculum content-section">
