               <h4 class="curriculum__subtitle"></h3>
               <div class="curriculum--flex-box">
                    <section class="class-offering">
                         <h5 class="curriculum__subtitle">In our Web Development fundamentals course, you will learn how to program with HTML, CSS and Javascript. We will teach you how to use Node.js and key node modules as well as OAuth 2.0, social authentication and how to create a subscription service.</h5>
                         <img class="class-offering__image"src="img/web.jpg" alt="">
                    </section>
                    <section class="class-offering">
                         <h4 class="class-offering__title">Web Track Projects</h4>
                         <h5 class="class-offering__title">Web Full Stack Fundamentals</h5>
