                              <li>Online Resume</li>
                              <li>Online Portfolio</li>
                              <li>Javascript Form</li>
                              <li>Saving to a Database</li>
                              <li>Blog or Trivia Game</li>
                              <li>Youtube or Soundcloud consolidation site</li>
